                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote>
                        <p>flattened palmette-type acroteria. within an arched niche is a banquet
                           scene. at the center, an unbearded man reclines on a kline, dressed in a
                           chiton and himation. the seated woman in a contemplative pose is probably
                           his wife; she wears a chiton and himation. at the man's feet, a servant
                           sits on a stool. on the architrave is the preserved Greek
                           inscription.</p>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
