               ΜΕΝΕΜΑΧΕΔΙΦΙΛΟΥ<lb n="1"/>
               ΧΡΗΣΤΕ ΧΑΙΡΕ<lb n="2"/>
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>Worthy Menemachos, son of Diphilos, farewell.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Menemachos, the deceased, is to be identified with the reclining figure.  
               the early imperial date of the monument is suggested by the broken bar of the alpha and the prominent serifs.</p>
         </div>
